# Vite env example (optional)
#
# If your environment blocks access to unpkg.com, serve web-ifc WASM locally.
# This repo copies the WASM into `public/web-ifc/` on `npm run dev/build`.
#
# Override (optional):
# VITE_WEB_IFC_WASM_PATH=/web-ifc/
# VITE_FRAGMENTS_WORKER_URL=/fragments-worker/worker.mjs
